Download the latest IDEA 11.1 EAP, install the latest Kotlin plugin and the Java project from here.

IDEA EAP: http://confluence.jetbrains.net/display/IDEADEV/IDEA+11.1+EAP
Kotlin plugin link: (just download the latest artifacts):
http://teamcity.jetbrains.com/viewLog.html?buildTypeId=bt345&buildId=lastSuccessful 
(select Artifacts and download Kotlin plugin)

When you create a project and open .kt file IDEA will prompt you to specify Kotlin runtime lib,
use the default location.
